metadata.name: Infinite Space of Wonder
metadata.description:
The Cosmic Insignificance collection aims to capture the beauty of realizing our minute role in the vast universe; that we as humans are all just specks of stardust on a small spinning blue ball, surrounded by a great unknown filled with more magic than we will ever comprehend.

"On a cosmic scale, our life is insignificant, yet this brief period when we appear in the world is the time in which all meaningful questions arise." 
-Paul Ricoeur
